## Disable driver that eventually pulls in EFI_EARLYCON.
## The earlycon is SO slow on Thinkpad T14 it takes 30s to boot kernel alone!
# CONFIG_SERIAL_8250 is not set

## Disable PC Speaker
# CONFIG_INPUT_PCSPKR is not set
